OL,4,CNoel Clarke: ITV drops drama Viewpoint
OL,5,Cafter allegations against star
OL,6, ITV has decided to pull the final
OL,7, episode of the drama Viewpoint after
OL,8, allegations of sexual harassment were
OL,9, made against its star, Noel Clarke.
OL,11,FThe broadcaster said on Friday it had
OL,12,F"a zero tolerance policy to bullying,
OL,13,Fharassment and victimisation".
OL,15,FThe Kidulthood and Doctor Who star, 45,
OL,16,Fhas said he "vehemently" denies "any
OL,17,Fsexual misconduct or wrongdoing".
OL,19,FIn a statement on Thursday, he said he
OL,20,Fintended to "defend myself against
OL,21,Fthese false allegations".
